    {
      "id": "c2722a220e53b1be90e4bf7433c28fd4e7863530",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 177,
        "name": "John Hammond",
        "email": "jhammond@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "jhammond"
      },
      "date": "2018-04-05 16:05:32.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nAmir, should we port this to 2.10?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "a401899c1eadb6a258f838f0400894e91dc744cb",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 125,
        "name": "James Simmons",
        "email": "jsimmons@infradead.org",
        "username": "jsimmons"
      },
      "date": "2018-04-05 16:23:10.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nSo the question is will 2.10 support MOFED 4.x and ARM systems? If not then their is no need to land this. If it is the case that these configurations are not supported then we need to let users know they need to move to a minimum lustre 2.11 for proper MOFED 4.X and ARM support. I will discuss this on the LWG call today.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "59dfc7b62ce05459a324c209bc6254d455c910d3",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 125,
        "name": "James Simmons",
        "email": "jsimmons@infradead.org",
        "username": "jsimmons"
      },
      "date": "2018-04-12 17:47:20.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: -Code-Review\n\nI talked to Amir about back porting these changes. Pretty much lustre 2.10 has what it needs to get MOFED 4.X working so to avoid the risk of regressions maybe only LU-9810 will be back ported but nothing else. Amir can comment as well.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "d57177edf20160579aef505a6c47348567dfea43",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 125,
        "name": "James Simmons",
        "email": "jsimmons@infradead.org",
        "username": "jsimmons"
      },
      "date": "2018-04-13 13:47:31.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\nSince Amir doesn't want this to land",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
